client
dev tun
proto udp
remote vpn.example.com 1194
resolv-retry infinite
nobind
remote-cert-tls server
cipher AES-256-GCM
auth SHA256
verb 3
<ca>
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
MIIBfakeCA...
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
</ca>
<cert>
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
MIIBfakeCert...charlie
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
</cert>
<key>
-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----
MIIBfakeKey...charlie
-----END PRIVATE KEY-----
</key>
